name: Amerta Sushi
address: Jl. Panji Sakti, Dauhwaru, Kec. Jembrana, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82218, Indonesia
review 1: Very good and calm place. Tasty sushi for a reasonable price. The owner is kind and welcoming man.
review 2: The best place to eat in Jembrana. Delicious sushi, welcoming host and cheap prices.
review 3: The sushi was very tasteful and the owner is very hospitable.  We enjoyed several dishes and we can recommend it.
review 4: Always love the takoyaki here. And my niece loves the burger! Calm place, definitely will come back~
